data.text: David and Ruth Eileen Beers Buckner will celebrate their 50th wedding anniversary on August 15, 2015. They are the parents of a daughter Kristine (husband Tim) Burke. They have 4 grandchildren, Logan, Joslyn, Kirsten & Nolan. They would enjoy hearing from their friends: David & Ruth Buckner, 9044 Northridge Ln., Battle Ground, IN 47920
